{"word":"H7250 - רָבַע - râbaʻ - raw-bah' - Let gender","slug":"H7250","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָבַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râbaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-bah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Let gender"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05D1;&#x05E2; - ra&#x0302;ba&#x201B;</b> - <i>raw-bah'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>squat</i> or <i>lie</i> out flat, that is, (specifically) in copulation: - let gender, lie down."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7252\">H7252</a>, <a href=\"#/H7254\">H7254</a>"}]}